  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.poster.avif?t=1746079522\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.webm?t=1746079522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.mp4?t=1746079522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game where you swing your weapon with the mouse to attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must rely on inertia and momentum to master the art of swinging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The screen is filled with monsters that also act as bullet hell; be careful to avoid them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is randomly generated, allowing you to play infinitely as the monsters grow stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your flipper skills; when the ball drops, it could turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill a large number of enemies to earn souls, which can be exchanged for soul potions to enhance your weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Content (Current Stage)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70+ weapons, with the ability to upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ items to boost your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out-of-game upgrades to enhance item capabilities.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.poster.avif?t=1746079522\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.webm?t=1746079522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518810/extras/1a90dca5ff1c631f9142d055907e7fed.mp4?t=1746079522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game where you swing your weapon with the mouse to attack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must rely on inertia and momentum to master the art of swinging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The screen is filled with monsters that also act as bullet hell; be careful to avoid them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is randomly generated, allowing you to play infinitely as the monsters grow stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your flipper skills; when the ball drops, it could turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill a large number of enemies to earn souls, which can be exchanged for soul potions to enhance your weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Content (Current Stage)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70+ weapons, with the ability to upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ items to boost your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out-of-game upgrades to enhance item capabilities.</p>",
